{"id": 3030, "date": "1987-02-16T11:00:48", "date_gmt": "1987-02-16T19:00:48", "guid": {"rendered": "http://estreetshuffle.com/?p=3030"}, "modified": "2026-06-09T10:01:21", "modified_gmt": "2026-06-09T17:01:21", "slug": "meeting-across-the-river-steve-earle-and-the-dukes-with-bruce-springsteen-sweet-virginia", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/1987/02/16/meeting-across-the-river-steve-earle-and-the-dukes-with-bruce-springsteen-sweet-virginia/", "title": {"rendered": "Sweet Virginia"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p>One time only, way back in February 1998: Bruce joined Steve Earle and The Dukes on stage at Tradewinds in Sea Bright, NJ to perform a &#8220;perfectly good British hillbilly song&#8221; by The Rolling Stones.</p>\n<div id=\"v-OBc9e2wc-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/OBc9e2wc?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p>This was Bruce&#8217;s one and only performance to date of &#8220;Sweet Virginia.&#8221; Here&#8217;s the original and still definitive by the Stones:</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/5R3xFy85fVE?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>Sweet Virginia<br />\nFirst performed:</strong> February 6, 1998 (Sea Bright, NJ)<br />\n<strong>Last performed:</strong> February 6, 1998 (Sea Bright, NJ)</p>\n<p>\u00a9 July 12, 2018</p>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>One time only: Bruce and Steve Earle team up on a Rolling Stones classic &#8220;British hillbilly song.&#8221;</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 69761, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "_jetpack_newsletter_access": "", "_jetpack_dont_email_post_to_subs": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_tier_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paywalled_content": false, "_jetpack_feature_clip_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content": false, "footnotes": "", "jetpack_publicize_message": "", "jetpack_publicize_feature_enabled": true, "jetpack_social_post_already_shared": true, "jetpack_social_options": {"image_generator_settings": {"template": "highway", "default_image_id": 0, "font": "", "enabled": false}, "version": 2}, "jetpack_post_was_ever_published": false}, "categories": [3617, 5], "tags": [81, 221, 1288], "class_list": ["post-3030", "post", "type-post", "status-publish", "format-standard", "has-post-thumbnail", "hentry", "category-it-takes-two", "category-meeting-across-the-river", "tag-rolling-stones", "tag-steve-earle", "tag-sweet-virginia"], "aioseo_notices": [], "jetpack_publicize_connections": [], "jetpack_featured_media_url": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/admin-ajax-2026-06-09T095947.769.jpg?fit=848%2C870&ssl=1", "jetpack_sharing_enabled": true, "jetpack_shortlink": "https://wp.me/p9w3Lk-MS", "jetpack_likes_enabled": true, "jetpack-re